Subject: Re: [T2] fan relay, switch

The relay is to detect if the alternator is charging or not...on a 72,
the fan will only run when the alternator is charging.   The switch up
front is only a contact which is made when you pull the right red lever
down.  (it grounds, completes the circuit, and turns the fan on)  g

